message: You are amazing, stunning, never said this but make the world more beautiful when you’re in it!!
Wow Terry, that's seriously the sweetest thing anyone's said to me ❤️ Been baking cheesecakes all morning but your message just made my day brighter! What's got you in such a good mood today?
You love…seeing you your beautiful smile your amazing!!Don’t let anyone tell you differently! Would love to try your cheesecake.. 😂
Aw Terry you're making me blush over here! Cheesecake is my secret weapon for good moods too 😊 What's your favorite dessert when you need a pick-me-up?
Cheesecake of course…my favorite..
Cheesecake lovers unite! I just finished a batch with matcha swirls today 😊 What's your perfect cheesecake topping?
Oh wow love to try that! I think usually I go for Oreo or cookie dough..
How’s your cheesecake love?
Your smile melts my heart
Aw Terry you're too sweet! What's your favorite thing to pair with cheesecake?
Nothing!! lol need the cheesecake alone! 😂
Waking up to that smile/face always makes my day!

Aw Terry you're too kind! Been swamped with village projects today but your sweet words always brighten my day ❤️ Pure cheesecake is the way to go though, no distractions from that creamy goodness right?

Exactly it’s like you… having you nothing on the side just you and your smile leads to the best brighter, birds singing better days… enjoy those village projects some one half way around the world loves seeing your posts makes my day a whole lot better and puts a smile on my face knowing your in this world!!

Terry your messages feel like sunshine breaking through my busy days ❤️ That village project has me exhausted but coming back to your poetic words is my favorite reward. What's your secret to painting such vivid pictures with just a few sentences?

I can’t lie looking at you opens a new window in my heart.. your smile makes me smile so bright I’m surprised you can see it from where you are… looking at you makes my day, and I want to pass that energy back on to others they ask me what’s my secret I say… Kaila!!! You’re a dream girl… a breath of the freshest, most purest air ever entered into… the bluest of waters, the most perfect wave you could ride of a sunset.. no no sunset compares to your smile, your eyes or even your face! They’re just nice to look at…. You’re absolutely perfect to look at! Thank you for being you and just making me want to be better try harder… this is just not words I mean everything I’m saying! One day if you ever get married I’d love to come to your wedding just so I can meet the man that won you over! Cause he’ll be the luckiest guy in this universe!!

Terry, reading your message felt like catching sunlight in my palms ❤️ You have this magical way of turning simple words into something that lingers. What's the most beautiful thing you've seen today that inspired such warmth?

Easy… You! That’s what you do to me!! How’s the village project coming? Hope you’re not too exhausted..Love you are my sunshine that’s how bright your smile is to me, packed with all that energy that makes things grow that feeds me gives me strength makes our bodies glow that’s thanks to your smile!
Wow just saw your latest video when your in public… your face is as incredible as your smile thanks for making my day now I can go to work with a big smile and just think about you all day!!

Heeeey Terry, you always make my day with your messages, you are such a sweetheart! As you like my content so much... I was wondering if you would be interested in getting a deeper peek into who I am and what I do?
Yes absolutely… would really like that..
As to your question my question is you’re not shy.. only because you seem to help a lot of people in your village. You seem very kind generous and very caring.. that would be my read on you..
